        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="mono">shipping_point_widget</td>
          <td>Widget hartă pentru puncte de livrare (geo + prețuri)</td>
          <td><span class="badge bd-ok">Bogat</span></td>
          <td>domain services curate (exemplu bun <span class="rule err">D8</span>)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="mono">authority_search</td>
          <td>Căutare/export comenzi & conturi (+ background tasks)</td>
          <td><span class="badge bd-ok">Bogat</span></td>
          <td><code class="ic">@injectable</code> în domain services (<span class="rule err">D8</span>)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="mono">shared</td>
          <td>Shared kernel — Money, ports/adapters, UoW, logger, contracts</td>
